{
  "texts": [
    "Since the UAV trajectory optimization can be regarded as an MDP, the DRL has been an effective method to deal with it [68].",
    "Qin et al. [244] investigated the joint design for UAV-ISAC networks, where multiple UAVs served as airborne ISAC-BSs to achieve dual services.",
    "They maximized the minimum weighted spectral efficiency through the joint trajectory of UAVs, user association, and power allocation design.",
    "Centralized and decentralized DRL algorithms were proposed to address their formulated problems.",
    "Tang et al. [245] investigated the UAV-assisted ISAC systems, where the UAV was used as an airborne ISAC node to sense multiple targets and upload the sensing data to the nearby ground BS."
  ]
}